'''''In to the Darkroom''''' is a 2014 short [[fiction film]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3924118/?ref_=nm_flmg_dr_1|title=	In to the Dark Room (2014)|publisher=IMDb.com|accessdate=17 February 2015}}</ref> which shows the glamor and then the bad side of [[smoking]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://shortfilmclub.org/in-to-the-darkroom-award-winning-short-film-2014-435/ |title=In to The Darkroom Award Winning Short Film 2014 4:35 &#124; |publisher=Shortfilmclub.org |date= |accessdate=17 February 2015}}</ref> The film tries to speak about the world of darkness and shadows which follows a smoker leading to a world of death. The film has won several National and international awards.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.manoramaonline.com/cgi-bin/MMOnline.dll/portal/ep/malayalamContentView.do?contentId=18144995&programId=3982928&channelId=-1073750705&BV_ID=@@@&tabId=3 |title=Movies &#124; News &#124; |publisher=Manorama Online |date= |accessdate=17 February 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.mathrubhumi.com/youth/features/%E0%B4%AA%E0%B5%81%E0%B4%95%E0%B4%B5%E0%B4%B2%E0%B4%BF-%E0%B4%B8%E0%B5%83%E0%B4%B7%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%9F%E0%B4%BF%E0%B4%95%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%95%E0%B5%81%E0%B4%A8%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%A8-%E0%B4%87%E0%B4%B0%E0%B5%81%E0%B4%9F%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%9F%E0%B5%8D-1.35569/ |title=Mathrubhumi Youth, Features പുകവലി സൃഷ്ടിക്കുന്ന ഇരുട്ട് |publisher=Mathrubhumi.com |date= |accessdate=17 February 2015}}</ref>

